<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>OTP Verification Email Template</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        display: relative;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .head {
        display: flex;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
        margin: auto;
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-style: initial;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #3e8e41;
      }
      .otp {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 40px;
        padding-right: 5px;
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border: solid #ccc 2px;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #232020;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .mail-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="head">Welcome to Autho</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= user.username %>,</p>
      <p>
        Thanku for registering with Autho. To activate your account, please use
        the following activation code:
      </p>
      <div class="otp"><%= activationCode %></div>
      <p>
        This OTP code will expire in 5 mins. If you did not request this code,
        please ignore this email.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for choosing Autho. We look forward to helping you achieve
        your goals!
      </p>
      <p>Sincerely,</p>
      <p>Aura and its team</p>

      <div class="mail-footer">
        If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at
        <a href="mailto:quotesf9@gmail.com">quotesf9@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
